Using Spring 3.2.8 and Java 7, gives this output:

    value of count:1
    com.spring3demo.account.repository.InMemoryAccountRepository@4da8692d
    com.spring3demo.account.repository.InMemoryAccountRepository@4da8692d
    value of count:2
    Using name value of: simulated Dynamic Parameter One
